name: Autovarrett Dragon
desc: When a Link Monster's effect is activated that targets this card (Quick Effect): You can destroy this card, then send 1 Spell/Trap on the field to the GY. During the End Phase, if this card is in the GY because it was destroyed by battle or card effect and sent there from the field this turn: You can Special Summon 1 "varrett" monster from your Deck, except "Autovarrett Dragon". You can only use each effect of "Autovarrett Dragon" once per turn.
